title: Buprofezin
label: Eco-Friendly
description: Buprofezin is a widely used agricultural insecticide effective in controlling sucking pests in crops.
It acts as an insect growth regulator (IGR), disrupting the molting process in nymphs and larvae.
Suitable for a variety of crops including cotton, vegetables, and ornamentals.
Storage: Keep in a cool, dry place away from children and pets. Dispose of containers responsibly.

title: Acetamiprid
label: Eco-Friendly
description: Acetamiprid is a general-purpose pesticide effective against a wide range of insects.

Suitable for use in fruits, vegetables, and ornamental plants.
Storage: Store in a cool, dry place away from sunlight and children.

title: Carbendazim
label: Eco-Friendly
description: Carbendazim is used for weed control and to protect crops against competing plants.
